data.description: Beautiful layout with 3 bedrooms and 3 baths, an office space + a den! The spacious floor plan and outdoor living spaces are perfect for entertaining guests. Step inside and enjoy a two-story entry, and large windows for great light. This home offers a seamless blend of comfort and functionality. The bedrooms provide ample room for relaxation, while the well-appointed bathrooms add convenience to everyday living. The additional office space offers endless possibilities for work or creative pursuits. With its modern amenities and thoughtful layout, this property is poised to elevate your living experience. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your dream home! Motivated seller!
